snippet.title: Powercity 9000 | New main menu screen (+ options) (alpha v1.1)
snippet.description:
This is a little video about Powercity 9000, showing the new main menu (still under construction!) and the new options.

Powercity 9000 is a game that we're working on,
enjoy!

*INFO*
Made with Monogame in Microsoft visual studio

*DOWNLOAD*
